{"tid":978210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"推理故掲尾故","createTime":"2019-01-11T17:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T15:51:19.000Z","uid":224141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"090ce5691f25be1396d023497dddd1bbd1c1ecbe","tid":978210,"uid":224141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:32:55.000Z","msg":"掲尾故<br />\n老爸的工作很私密，所以就算我們住在同一間房子也分了樓層睡。有一天，我工作回家打算到二樓叫老爸一起食飯，咦不在家？老爸平日這樣夜是不會到外面去的。算了睡吧，是到外出吧。<br />\n過了一星其了 ，到老爸朋友家，公司問了都沒有消息，失蹤了。<br />\n我報了警，警察搜索了也沒有消息。<br />\n有一天，我在老爸的二樓桌上看到了有一些似是字的塵，S.. O?<br />\n我摸了一下，手指上沾了塵和紅色的污積，是什麼？是吃完食物留下的汁液？<br />\n又過了一個月，我無意中找到了老爸的日記本？！！有失蹤當日的日記？！！！！！！什麼！<br />\n<br />\nonly yes or no question"},{"pid":"acf04b4a6b707ab83e5fd653d1600ec4c86dfaa5","tid":978210,"uid":159444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:49:59.000Z","msg":"用血寫？sos?"},{"pid":"5cb13854c6aad11662191580498e4e75ca09f060","tid":978210,"uid":174906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:06:46.000Z","msg":"老爸已死了？"},{"pid":"c5e141f0cce66181a6a9affd66dc5e738acf6f9c","tid":978210,"uid":224141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acf04b4a6b707ab83e5fd653d1600ec4c86dfaa5","tid":978210,"uid":159444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T17:49:59.000Z","msg":"用血寫？sos?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"no, yes"},{"pid":"995fa189aad839cbd68ee2e4f5874d83248d2a1f","tid":978210,"uid":224141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cb13854c6aad11662191580498e4e75ca09f060","tid":978210,"uid":174906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:06:46.000Z","msg":"老爸已死了？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:13:51.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"ecb4588bb28acdd7770435551a2aba29f2352b30","tid":978210,"uid":112065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:28:57.000Z","msg":"樓豬癡線？有兄弟姐妹？"},{"pid":"73b87b003049ef41b644cce052ea4c986130fe81","tid":978210,"uid":11349